data.description: Come see it in person to see all this home offers and the community!! This is a beautiful Taylor Morrison "Elmhurst I" listing in the highly desirable community of Channing Park. Freshly painted exterior-done!  LET'S TALK SOLAR PANELS! Is your current electric bill too expensive? This home will provide you with the lowest electric bill you will ever pay. Having this added solar system will allow you tap into these solar energy advantages and improve your homes value. This home offers 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths. Upon entering, the foyer is inviting with accent walls, laminate flooring leading to the formal living room and dining room. This home has a triple split floor plan with a bedroom and full bath towards the front of the home, two bedrooms and full bath towards the center, and the master bedroom and bath located on the backside of the home. Step into the kitchen and check out all the modern updates this kitchen has been given; 42 inch wall cabinets, quartzite countertops, decorative tile backsplash, wood butcher block tabletop on island, stainless steel single basin sink, touchless faucet, air switch garbage disposal, reverse osmosis water filtration system, and an under-counter wine cabinet to hold all your adult beverages. Newer stainless steel refrigerator, dishwasher, and gas range. The breakfast bar is adjacent to the family room that has luxury plank flooring, where you can sit and enjoy the natural lighting from your windows and sliders leading out to the covered lanai. The master bedroom is spacious and has luxury plank flooring, his and her walk in closets, and the master bath is tastefully designed with granite counter tops, dual sinks, garden tub with jets, separate shower stall with tile, and en suite bathroom. The backyard is fully fenced with plenty of room for your own pool, swing set, or playhouse. The possibilities are endless. Step inside your garage that's been finished with epoxy flooring and updated tankless gas water heater. Channing Park offers wonderful amenities and include the Pirate Splash Pad, heated resort style pool, spa, kiddie pool, fitness center, clubhouse with gas grills, soccer/volley ball/football field, basketball courts, skate park, playground, dog park, and picnic area! So much to enjoy in this community. Great location near Fish Hawk Ranch/Park Square and easy commute into Valrico, Brandon, Tampa, MacDill AFB. Enjoy plenty of restaurants and shops nearby. Make your appointment today and come get a closer look for yourself!
